ygData.subject: Favorite Ranger Quest at lvl 38 ?
ygData.msgSnippet: Hey folks, Just wanted to know if anyone had some good quests ideas to do at lvl 38 as a ranger. Just did the cougarskin mask (AC6 +2agi +2dex +10hp)
ygData.messageBody:
Hey folks,<br><br>Just wanted to know if anyone
had some good quests ideas to do at lvl 38 as a
ranger. Just did the cougarskin mask (AC6 +2agi +2dex
+10hp) and direwolf cloak (AC7 +5str) quest last night
in Iceclad. Very easy and the items are pretty good
considering the ease of aquiring the correct items. They
certainly beat the banded armor items i was
wearing.<br><br>I think im next going to my enchanted bow quest.
Seems pretty easy for the most part with the exception
of killing the mermaid in Kedge. <br><br>all ideas
and suggestions are open )
